HEADWORD: Menispermaceous
<hw>Men`i*sper*ma"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>mh`nh</grk> the moon + <grk>spe`rma</grk> seed.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to a natural order
